%% Title
%% Door Access System Architecture (Polling Model)

PWA[PWA / Browser\nMember UI]

API[Symfony API\n\nControllers:\nAccessController\nDeviceController\nAccessConfirmController\n\nServices:\nOpenDoorService\nDoorJobService\nAccessRequestService\nAccessService]

DB[(Database\n\nContao Core:\ntl_member\ntl_member_group\n\nCommunity Offers:\ntl_co_access_request\ntl_co_device\ntl_co_door_job\ntl_co_door_log)]

DEVICE[Raspberry Pi\n\nPull-Client\nToken Auth\n\nPoll + Confirm]

GATEWAY[Shelly / Relay\nDoor Actuator]

%% Door opening flow

PWA -->|POST /api/door/open/:area| API

API -->|create job\nstatus=pending| DB

%% Device polling loop

DEVICE -->|POST /api/device/poll| API

API -->|dispatch job\nstatus=dispatched| DEVICE

DEVICE -->|execute door action| GATEWAY

DEVICE -->|POST /api/device/confirm| API

API -->|update status\nexecuted/failed/expired| DB

%% Access request flow

PWA -->|Access Request Form| API

API -->|create access request| DB

API -->|send DOI mail| PWA

PWA -->|Confirm DOI Token| API

API -->|assign member groups| DB

%% Architecture constraints

DEVICE -.->|No inbound connections\nPull only| API

API -.->|confirmWindow configured| DEVICE

API -.->|poll interval ~2s| DEVICE
